Today's Stratechery Interview is with Manna Founder and CEO Bobby Healy ( h=
ttps://x.com/realbobbyhealy ). Manna ( https://www.manna.aero/ ) , based in=
 Ireland, builds and operates delivery drones; Manna started with the Dubli=
n suburbs and is in the process of expanding to other European cities. The =
company has made over 150,000 deliveries, and its most popular product is a=
 cup of coffee.

I thought this interview was fascinating. Healy walks me through the entire=
