ed and the under-appreciated part of Google I think. They have a fantastic =
aircraft, great team, same vision as us, and we work very closely together.=
 We cooperate in all sorts of areas to move things forward.

Will we go to war? Of course we will, and it's a big enough market. Like I =
said, forget about food delivery. We want to move everything. Every single =
thing that customers get to their house we want to be carrying it for them.=
 So this is trillions of dollars of value, I'd be happy to share half of th=
at with Google, maybe even a little bit less than half.

